process.title: What is GDSC WOW
process.description: Experience the pinnacle of tech innovation at GDSC WOW MANGALURU, an esteemed event orchestrated by Google Developer Student Clubs (GDSC) in Mangaluru. Join us as we unite students, developers, and industry mavens to delve into the cutting-edge realms of technology and uncover the latest trends shaping our digital landscape.

process.title: Where and when will GDSC WOW MANGLURU take place?
process.description: GDSC WOW MANGALURU is scheduled to take place at Srinivas Institute Of Technology (S.I.T), located in Valachil, Mangaluru, Karnataka, India. Mark your calendars for May 6th, 2024, from 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM IST.

process.title: What kind of individuals can join GDSC WOW
process.description: GDSC WOW Mangaluru extends its welcome to students, developers, and technology enthusiasts, fostering an inclusive environment for those eager to delve into learning, networking, and immersing themselves in the vast expanse of technology.

process.title: What can I expect at GDSC WOW ?
process.description: GDSC WOW MANGALURU will feature a diverse range of activities including tech talks, workshops, hands-on coding sessions, networking opportunities, and more. It's a chance to learn from industry experts, connect with peers, and gain valuable insights into the world of technology.

process.title: Sponsorship or partnership opportunities for GDSC WOW
process.description: Certainly! Feel free to connect with us if you're interested in partnering or sponsoring GDSC WOW MANGALURU. You can find our contact details on our website for further inquiries and collaboration opportunities.

process.title: How can I stay updated with GDSC WOW MANGALURU announcements?
process.description: To stay updated with the latest news and announcements about GDSC WOW MANGALURU, make sure to follow us on our social media handles and regularly check our website for updates.
